Summary: 5 circular objects one bigger and spinning crossed mission bay and the 5 free way coming from the west in low altitude and headed south and up until they complete disappeared
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in my car when i saw five circle objects cross the mission bay coming from the west in low altitude. There was a bigger one that i could see clearly spinning and blinking different lights! The other 4 objects were smaller and had one color only! The 5 objects hovered for a little bit on top of the free way, so they started heading south and up in the sky until they complete disappeared really hight in the sky!
